<li id="cite_note-20"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-20">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Burkert 1983:201)</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-21"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-21">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Stewart Flory, "Arion's Leap: Brave Gestures in Herodotus" <i>The American Journal of Philology</i> <b>99</b>.4 (Winter 1978:411-421).</span>
</li>
</ol></div></div>
